{"tid":751564,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲識解夢","createTime":"2018-07-22T04:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T09:32:44.000Z","uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3822dd25df61863ec159d2cee6cda67e1de4df9c","tid":751564,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T04:25:11.000Z","msg":"話說我琴晚就發咗個夢覺得好困擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望有巴打絲打可以幫到我解讀吓係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前言<br />\n我有女朋友嘅  <br />\n仲有一個幾friend嘅女仔friend叫a女<br />\n咁佢地就唔識對方嘅<br />\n而我女朋友就成日都妒忌a女嘅<br />\n都因為咁鬧過唔少交同埋差啲分手<br />\n<br />\n正題<br />\n其實我都唔係記得好清楚個夢嘅詳細<br />\n但係記得好深嘅一幕係同a女一齊嘅<br />\n佢就挨落我度叫我鍚佢<br />\n而我當時係攬住a女嘅<br />\n跟住我喺夢入面就好掙扎唔知點好<br />\n今朝好早醒咗煩惱到宜家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我係咪變咗心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔想做賤男做仆街仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da5f46575acdc9c1ee9d3543516e2793878fac3","tid":751564,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T04:28:53.000Z","msg":"諗太多"},{"pid":"484ed19a906aa11178741a029cbc3642d63b116d","tid":751564,"uid":130162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T04:30:21.000Z","msg":"你問得岀<br />\n姐係你對你個女仔fd既感覺已經超越左普通朋友"},{"pid":"4893ac36afb33af3f57b3956df14878c92d62051","tid":751564,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"484ed19a906aa11178741a029cbc3642d63b116d","tid":751564,"uid":130162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T04:30:21.000Z","msg":"你問得岀<br />\n姐係你對你個女仔fd既感覺已經超越左普通朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T04:40:56.000Z","msg":"我唔識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩個人我都好重視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09e340b99b7727e16fd200789a258b643058a02","tid":7515